#: ../../source/kv_cache/caching_policies.rst:2
msgid "Using Different Caching Policies"
msgstr "使用不同的缓存策略"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/caching_policies.rst:4
msgid "LMCache supports multiple caching policies."
msgstr "LMCache 支持多种缓存策略。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/caching_policies.rst:6
msgid ""
"For example, to use LRU, you can set the environment variable "
"``LMCACHE_CACHE_POLICY=LRU`` or set it in the configuration file with "
"``cache_policy=\"LRU\"``."
msgstr "例如，要使用 LRU，您可以设置环境变量 ``LMCACHE_CACHE_POLICY=LRU`` 或在配置文件中设置 ``cache_policy=\\\"LRU\\\"``。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/caching_policies.rst:8
msgid ""
"Currently, LMCache supports \"LRU\" (Least Recently Used), \"MRU\" (Most "
"Recently Used), \"LFU\" (Least Frequently Used) and \"FIFO\" (First-In-"
"First-Out) caching policies."
msgstr "目前，LMCache 支持 \\\"LRU\\\"（最近最少使用）、\\\"MRU\\\"（最近最多使用）、\\\"LFU\\\"（最不常用）和 \\\"FIFO\\\"（先进先出）缓存策略。"


#: ../../source/kv_cache/caching_policies.rst:1
msgid "This page documents the behavior of LMCache's in-process mode (deprecated). Please consider using :doc:`LMCache MP mode </mp/index>` for better feature support and performance."
msgstr "本页面介绍 LMCache 进程内模式（不推荐使用）的行为。建议改用 :doc:`LMCache MP 模式 </mp/index>`\\ 以获得更好的功能支持与性能。"
